title: 18 - Megan Gailey
itunes:title: 18 - Megan Gailey
description: Megan Gailey is a longtime buddy and first time 5 words podcast guest. You’ve seen her on Comedy Central and Just For Laughs, now listen to her with us in the All Things Comedy studio. We’re talking Instagram babies, Megan’s engagement, Reggie Miller, shitty airports, and Shakespeare. Here’s five words to describe this episode: it isn’t in iambic pentameter.
